Dialogs.Dialog: Look. I cut my hair. How do you like it？
Look. I go a haircut. Any opinions？
Look. I shortened my hair. Do you think it looks good？
Hey, I changed the length of my hair. What do you think？
Not really my cup of tea
Hey. This hair length isn't weird, right？
My hair has grown a lot longer, how do you like it？
You know, my hair has grown quite a bit. Does it suit me？
Hey？ I grew my hair long. It's not weird, right？
I see. You like it. I thought so.
I see, I see. Do you really like it？ I knew you would say that.
Hehe. I knew you would say that. Thanks.
Huh？ I thought you might like this kind of thing...
What, you didn't like it？ I though...
I thought you would like it, haha...
I kind of rearranged my hair.
I like how fresh it is！
Can you see？ This is a new version of my hair.
Hey, I tried to arrange my hair. Do you think it looks good？
That's good then. I might make this a regular thing.
I see. You still like it？ Just as I thought.
Haha... I shouldn't have tried so hard.
No way. I thought it was cute...
Look. I changed my hair color.
Ah, your image has really changed...
Hey. Do you think this hair color looks good on Rinko？
I thought it would be a nice change of pace... So I tried this color.
My vibe has changed completely with this. How do you like it？
I was thinking "is this color fresh？". Is it not？
I thought I'd change up my outfit a bit...
Today Rinko changed the vibe of her clothes, didn't she？
Hey, how does Rinko look？ I think it changed the vibe of my clothes.
I intended to make my clothes neat and tidy... What do you think？
How do you like it？ It gives and adult vibe.
I'm trying to be what's called a neat and tidy type, how do you like it？
I guess that's what it's like
I can't believe I'm saying this myself, but it's a cute outfit, right？
Today Rinko is cute. Do you like it？
Do casual clothes look good on me...？
This kind of casual stuff is surprisingly difficult. What do you think？
It looks good you on you！
Hey. How about a casual looking Rinko？
I tried something more mature... Is it weird？
I though I would try something a little more mature... What do you thing？
Now Rinko has a little more sex appeal...？ No？
Really？ Then I'll dress like this from now on.
If you like it, I'll keep you in the loop.
Then I'm glad. I'm going to keep it this way from now on♪
What's that... If you don't like it, then forget it.
You don't have to say it that way... You idiot！
Ehh... I thought you liked this kind of thing.
Hah... You should react a little more quickly.
What... I thought you'd be more than happy.
I see... you're not really interested？ Hah.
Well, what do you think of today's outfit？ I think it's very adult-like.
Well, let's hear your thoughts today, shall we？ Just in case.
Ah, so that's how it is？
I've made it neat and tidy again today. What do you think？
I'm worried about whether cute clothes of this type look good on me...
Don't I look girlier in today's clothes？
Hey, how about this for today？
I think I'll keep my clothes like this. It's easy to do.
Why don't you try something different？
Is this the kind of clothes you like now？ This is kind of a rough look.
Rinko's clothes aren't weird, are they？ I think it's casual.
I see. Well, that's fine then.
You what？ I thought you would say that.
Good for you. I like being praised. Hehe.
I see. You like different thing. Tell me sooner.
What, you're acting high and mighty. Well, I get it.
I see... I'll try to get some compliments next time.
Be clear. The quest is, is it good or bad？
Geez. Don't you have more to say？
